Package org.araneaframework.uilib.list.util.comparator

Interface Summary
StringComparator General interface for Comparator that compares String objects.
 

Class Summary
BooleanComparator Not-null comparator that compares Boolean values.
ComparableComparator Not-null comparator that compares Comparable objects by their own (@see java.lang.Comparable#compareTo(java.lang.Object)) method.
IgnoreCaseComparator Not-null comparator that compares String values case insensitive.
LocaleStringComparator Not-null comparator that compares String values according to the Locale and case sensitive option.
NullComparator Comparator that compares null values and uses another not-null Comparator in other cases.
ReverseComparator Comparator that reverses another Comparator by switching the order of two comparable objects.
